      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly 'as-is,' making it an ideal project car or a source for parts. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-idling engine and a transmission that slips between gears. The body has heavy rust on the rocker panels, a cracked windshield, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. While it does start, it will require a trailer for transport and substantial work to be roadworthy again.",
