    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical repairs, as the engine struggles to stay running and the transmission is slipping badly. Externally, there is visible rust along the wheel wells and several large dents on the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be a suitable project for a mechanic or a source for spare parts.",
